DESCRIPTION:Reach out to your dealer to confirm timing and availability\n\n
 Issuer: SIBANYE STILLWATER LTD (SBSW)\nRoadshow: NetRoadshow presentation 
 with voiceover recording available\n\nDeal context:\nSibanye-Stillwater UK
  Financing Plc\, a wholly owned subsidiary of South African mining group S
 ibanye-Stillwater (JSE: SSW / NYSE: SBSW\, rated Ba2/BB/BB)\, is launching
  a US$500MM WNG 144A/Reg S Senior Unsecured Note offering with a 5.5NC2 st
 ructure\, with proceeds expected to support concurrent tender offers for S
 tillwater Mining Company's outstanding 4.0% Notes due 2026 (any and all) a
 nd 4.5% Notes due 2029 (capped at US$75MM). The deal is at the Mandate sta
 ge\, with a Global Investor Call scheduled for 14:30 UK / 09:30 NY on Wedn
 esday\, 6 May 2026\, followed by hybrid fixed income investor meetings in 
 London\, with BofA Securities\, Mizuho\, Morgan Stanley\, Rand Merchant Ba
 nk\, and RBC Capital Markets acting as Global Coordinators and Joint Bookr
 unners\; no pricing terms have been disclosed and the offering remains sub
 ject to market conditions.
